      "span_text": "Automatic Barcode Gap Discovery analysis [CITATION_1] , was processed using the \"graphic\" web version available at http://wwwabi.snv.jussieu.fr/public/abgd/abgdweb.html, under the default parameters of P min = 0.001 to P max = 0.1, steps = 10, X (relative gap width) = 1.5, Nb bins (for distance distribution) = 20, and the Kimura (K80) molecular model."
